# Media — encrypted files and manifest are tracked in git
# Plaintext media (images, PDFs, videos) must NEVER be committed
content/media/*
!content/media/*.enc
!content/media/manifest.json
!content/media/README.md
# Large media files (> 2MB) go to large/ — backed up via GitHub Releases
!content/media/large/
content/media/large/*
